Some respondents left the survey. Attrition can be monitored within the next query. 

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
gss_panel10_long |> 
  select(wave, id) |>
  group_by(wave) |>
  summarize(observed = n_distinct(id),
            missing = sum(is.na(id)))
```

